* This is my first Ruby on Rails web app. It is a simple app that takes a drink name and temperature and stores it on a data base.
* It is a Railsbridge Installfest sample app that can be implemented by following the steps at http://installfest.railsbridge.org/installfest/
* I hosted it on Heroku - a free cloud application platform. You can access it at https://hidden-dusk-5931.herokuapp.com